Small LAN with KALi 

Booting into Kali 
  Plug in USB
  Go into BIOS>boot order> make USB first in boot order
  Press F10 to save and load into bootable USB
  Select Live Kali to load into OS
 
Setting IP
  Click the drop down in the top right corner
  select Wired Connection>settings>Settings symbol>IPv4
  Set IP
